ice` 的连接有关，如“connection error: desc = transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup shippingservice”。\n\n2. **Redis服务性能问题**\n   - `cartservice->redis`的调用在操作如HMSET上出现异常，耗时从1,573微秒激增至19,776微秒。\n\n3. **异常错误传播路径**\n   - 在多个调用链中均有“shipping quote failure: failed to get shipping quote”的错误信息，其来源为 `checkoutservice` 与 `ShippingService` 的连接失败。\n   - 错误的初始发生点常见于 `frontend` 到 `checkoutservice`，表示错误从最前端请求开始传播。\n\n这些发现指向 `ShippingService` 的连接问题可能是根本原因，导致上游服务例如 `CheckoutService` 出现延迟，并影响最终的用户请求响应。\n\n### 下一步\n在后续阶段，我们将深入分析这些异常，以确定具体的根因和可能的修复策略。\n\n### JSON输出格式\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"redis->cartservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"connection error rate and increased response time\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Increased response time due to failed ShippingService connection\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"server_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"region_pending\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"The checkoutservice-1 exhibited significant increase in both error_ratio and server_error_ratio, which directly impacts the response time and service availability.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio from 0.0 to 45.22 and server_error_ratio from 0.0 to 45.22 with a p99_change_ratio of 2.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"The shippingservice-0 showed an increase in client_error_ratio, which could lead to network related issues affecting service response.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 31.66 with a change r